VCS/Lite version 0.02
=====================

This is the initial version of VCS::Lite. Algorithm::Diff needs to
be installed first.


To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Algorithm::Diff

